name: Shoes
description: Shoes is the key to a complete look. Help them achieve it by giving a pair of shoes!

name: Sport Shoes
description: He/she loves sports more than anything? We have a winning gift right here!

name: High Heels
description: Nice pair of heels is always nice to wear and nice to find in a gift box!

name: Shirt
description: Every man and every boy needs unlimited amount of shirt for every possibility everyday.

name: Dress
description: Don't know what to give to a sweet girl who likes to dress up? A dress it is!

name: Jeans
description: You will never go wrong with jeans. Always useful, they'll be grateful.

name: Text Book
description: Whether it's a student or someone who just loves to study, text book is all you need.

name: Comic Book
description: Who says comic books are kid's stuff? But it's nice to give to kids too, so everyone wins!

name: Novel
description: He/she carries books everywhere? Give them something to read, novel is your go-to!

name: Music CD
description: Music makes people happy. And sometimes it costs quite some so you will help a lot with this.

name: Movie DVD
description: Promised someone to watch a movie but never get the chance to? Problem solved.

name: Handphone
description: Strengthen your bond with a clearer communication, get a brand new cellphone.

name: Ring
description: Well, if you like it then you should put a ring on it. Let's take it to the next level.

name: Homemade Cooking
description: Nothing says a sincere gift like foods made by none other than you. Spread the love with every bite.

name: Chocolate
description: May it be a sweet gift for anniversary, or just a bribe to stop your loved one from sulking, chocolate will always be the answer.

name: Cake
description: Why cake is the perfect gift? Because it's delicioous, everyone loves it, and it's delicious.

name: Flower
description: Girls love flower. Why don't you love giving it? It's affordable and easy to find!

name: Kitchen Utensil
description: For someone who loves cooking, it can't be any more perfect gift than this.

name: Make Up
description: Woman can't have too many make-up. Even if you see them stacking, there will always be room for more.

name: Plushie
description: Cuddly toy to accompany them during the night? Get one of these cute dolls!

name: Pampering Set
description: With a lot of stress and hectic schedule, help them relax by giving this.

name: Wallet
description: Wallet is always the right gift to every age, every gender, every situation.

name: Watch
description: You will be remembered every time they check time time. It could be every 5 seconds.

name: Tie
description: An easy way to complete a formal look. Classic? Colorful? There's one for every personality!

name: Self-Painting
description: Show they are in your eyes. Low painting skills? Don't worry, it's the thought that counts.

name: Sunglasses
description: Bright sunlight that bothers their sight? Not a problem!

name: Fine Dining
description: Splurge a little bit more in a special day for an unforgettable fancy dining!

name: Guitar
description: Release the inner musician inside of them. Who knows, it might earn them extra cash.

name: Idol Collectibles
description: Posters? Postcards? Photobooks? Anything with the idol's face on it, they'll love it.

name: Camera
description: Capture every precious moments that they have. Some might even incude you!

name: Stationary Set
description: Useful gift and so helpful to everyone who needs to write down stuff in daily basis.

name: Hamster
description: Learn taking responsibilities in a fun way. Cute hamster can be the right way to do it!
